TARGET.NAME: GMSA_HBU_WK_SHIP_ERR

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping loads the HBU Weekly shipment errors to target
MAPPING.NAME: m_GMSA_HBU_WK_SHIP_ERR

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Filter transformation to filter the select data for AMT < Reference_sub_key_2
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FIL_GMSA

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Aggregate the Header names so that only one row for the header have been populated
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_HEADER

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joiner transformation to join the GMSA & EDM.dbo.Reference tables
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_GMSA_REFERENCE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source query to get data from EDM.dbo.Reference table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Reference

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select Reference_sub_key_1, CONVERT(INT,Reference_sub_key_2) Reference_sub_key_2 from EDM.dbo.Reference where Reference_key='SambaHBUCheck'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Hardcode the ERROR MESSAGE to the target file
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_GMSA_HBU_WK_SHIP_ERR

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Reads HBU Weekly shipment Error Records from the Source table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_GROSS_MARGIN_STYLE_ACCOUNT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select slba_division_code,hbu, sum(amt) amt,sum(pamt) pamt from ( Select slba_division_code, case when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code='20' then 'PL' when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code!='20' then 'BA' else g.slba_division_code end hbu ,sum(g.dollars) amt,0 pamt from slba.gross_margin_style_account g where g.as_of_date = ( select d.as_of_date-7 from slba.day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate)) and g.slba_division_code !='DS' and g.sales_measure_name='Gross OS' group by slba_division_code,case when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code='20' then 'PL' when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code!='20' then 'BA' else g.slba_division_code end
union Select slba_division_code, case when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code='20' then 'PL' when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code!='20' then 'BA' else g.slba_division_code end hbu ,0 amt,sum(g.dollars) pamt from slba.gross_margin_style_account g where g.as_of_date = ( select d.as_of_date-14 from slba.day_dimension d where d.day_date=trunc(sysdate)) and g.slba_division_code !='DS' and g.sales_measure_name='Gross OS' group by slba_division_code, case when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code='20' then 'PL' when g.slba_division_code = 'IN' and g.company_code!='20' then 'BA' else g.slba_division_code end ) group by slba_division_code,hbu
